text:
Bhai tujhe jaan ke maza bohot aaya hai. Tere jokes ki delivery aur timing ekdum perfect hoti hai. Ofcourse tu dancer toh acha hai hi. Humlog shayad wing ke context ke bahar bohot zyada hang out kiye nahi hai, but you are a fun person to chill out with! Stay cool, keep dancing, and let the girls chase you ;)
Also bhai wing calls pe hi sahi but lets stay in touch. Live long and prosper!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Hum dost hain ki nahi pata nahi, par bhai zarur hain. Yaar baaten toh hazaaron hain yahan likhne ko jo apan Hall 5 me ghoom ghoom ke karte the, par wo saari rehne hi deta hu, kyuki tujhe sabkuch yaad rehta hi hai xD Apne rishtay pe kabhi 4 laine likhi thi, wahi chipka raha hu firse -

text: CSE ke stud launde ko salaam _/\_ Bhai tindal tune toh mujhe ek alag hi duniya dikhayi hai xD Umeed hai uss duniya se rishta bana rahega aur shayad wahin firse milenge hum kabhi :P
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Pandeyji ko pranam! _/\_
Sir aapse bada inspiration toh IITK Y17 me koi hoga hi nahi. Aapki jitni tareef kare kum hai. Aapka all round knowledge aur intellect IITK ke itihaas aur hamaze zehen me hamesha zinda rahega. Thoda dukh hua tha sunke aapke Civil Service ki ichchha chod di hai, umeed karte hain ki ye aag kahin fir se jage aur aap desh ko bhi apne jaisi unnati dein!
Jis tarah 4 saal aapne humpe kripa banayi hai waise hi aage banaye rakhen. Samay samay aapko hum yaad kar liya karenge, darshan aur gyaan avashya de dijiyega. Iske liye aapka abhi se aabhar!
Bhavadiya,
Kothari
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Gulati yaar tumhara wo Antaragni wala plan successful ho jaata na IITK life hi sidhdhh ho jaati :P
Hummne kaafi saara samay sath me nikala hai RM me, aur kaafi maza aaya hai tumse baaten karke both in and outside pclub. At one point RM toh hamara permanent home bann hi gaya tha. RM me raat ko AC chalu karna, KD wala wo room aur Blackbox ke samay ka wo pizza sab bohot hi fun tha. Some of the best philosophical conversations I have had have been with you. Kuch cheezen karni thi jo reh gayi, kabhi Amsterdam ya California me koi plan banate hain. Also Maine zyada tareef kari nahi tumhari but you know I know you are exteremly intelligent :P
Touch me rehna :)
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Jai Shiv Shambhu!
Mishraji aapko yaad hai kya hamare paas ke Jharkhand Union ka slack hai? Ab college khatam ho gaya hai toh uspe thoda active hote hain wapas kya kehte hain?
Baaki Mishraji aapke sath toh kaafi mazze kiye hain, shivji ki bhakti jo sikhayi hai aapko yaad rakhiyega aur naye mantra seekhne ke liye milte hain kahbi, koi trip plan karke. CP, Antaragni, CSE, aur aapka dhep apping xD humne 4 saalon me kaafi kuch kiya hai sath me, lekin thoda aur kar zarur sakte the.
Aapko shayad yaad na ho 3rd sem me NCL ke terrace pe aap aur mai galti se mil gaye the aur ek bohot motivating converstaion hua tha apne beech uske liye thanks! :)

Baaki apna toh chalta rahega, aur agar aap apna US wala long term plan execute karenge toh mujhe assistant rakh lijiyega please
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: Bhai sem 5 ka end, Mai tu Anish, thoda sa mango, pyaare gaane aur bohot saara khaana; wo raat hamesha yaad rahegi!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Hey Palindrome Roll Number guy,
Fresher's inferno tennis jeete the hum (all credit to you xD ). Baaki 1st year CPA ke baad bhi apni thodi bohot baaten toh ho hi jaati thi Narayan ki canteen me. Tumhare all round sports skills toh kabiliyat tareef hain, aur tumhara humble practical attitude kaafi commendable hai.
Asehi full of spirit rehna, kabhi tennis court pe milte hain thode tips de dena!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Narayan ki canteen ka cake competition yaad hai na? For future reference : use cold drink for lubrication (throat not soldier) :P
Thank you for TA201 CAD model, and that half a joint when I was out xD Your Bojack poster was super cool! Have a good life and create amazing machines. Milte hain kabhi cake khane!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Sir AIR10,
Anany tu ekdum ideal raha hai college me. Truly the only person I have known who can be called the jack of all trades. Grades, bakchodi, bulla, dance, mazze, tu hai real inspiration mere liye. Baaki mishra aur CSE ke beech apan bhi thoda bohot hangout toh kar hi liye. Hall2 canteen, KD, Misrha ka room aur Hall5 terrace :P Keep in touch bhai bohot seekhna hai terese aage! _/\_
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Bhai bhai bhai BHAI!!

Gravity se leke teri gaand tak kya kuch nahi dekha hai 4 saal me xD Bohot saaari memories hain apni toh. Grateful for all your advice and inputs on everything over the years. Chemical se Batti se CSE se Maths ki teri journey kaafi tough par achi rahi hai maine dekha hai. Bhai source bethao ghar pe scene banane ka yaar mera bhi apna toh tumne badiya set karliya hai. Telegram pe baat karte hain :P
Amsterdam chalo kabhi sath me
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Sanghi sir, charan sparsh _/\_
First-year ke end me tune bola tha ki 1st year me kaafi chill maar liya ab kaam karta hu pel ke.. fast forward three years.. lo and behold companies are dying to hire you. Mad respect for your dedication and skill and commitment man. Tujhe kaafi indulge karane ki koshish ki tune kabhi interest liya nahi :P Mishrsa se kuch seekh ek baar toh Shiv bhakti dekhni thi tujhe yaar. Aman ko toh ekdum maa ki tarah paala hai bhai tune. Teri bandi ka kya scene tha bhai tune theek se clear kiya nahi mai puchta reh gaya xD Goes without saying that we will be in touch. Kripa banaye rakhna!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: Greetings Ojha sir from neighboring Ranchi. Long conversations, misty indulgence(s), shared insecurities, non-human sleeping positions. After 4 years of IITK, I don't really have much to say to you. Glad to have known you well, enjoyed all our arguments and debates. We have definitely hung out a lot but still, we could definitely have hung out a lot more. You're a real fucker (in a good way). Also, tf man you screwed me by telling someone from BIT Mersa about a private conversation we had that found its way back to me through a relevant third party. Real pain in the ass. Definitely going to kick your ass for it someday. Lets meet soon!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Anish Sex hai na? (sorry PJ)
Okaaaay anish, youre okay dude. ABS, Pclub, H2 canteen, Pinku ka prasad aur mango ka swaad, Silent Disco are just some of the things I can remember, oh and Pizzas during blackbox in NCL. Its been swell man, Would have been nice agar tu EPFL aata but have fun in the US! Keep in touch milenge zarur!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
CHM101 yaad hi hoga? Gurunath ne kya bhagaya tha tumko lab me paani pene ke liye still makes me chuckle xD Didnt really talk much after that I think but idher udher mil hi jaate the kabhi kabhi. You're pretty outgoing, which I think is quite nice. Clear cut, straight forward, I like that. Thoda bolti zyada ho but okay :P Thank you for some of the advice you've given me and you're welcome for MTH102 in Library!
Cheers!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
That MH chick was cute yaar tune baat karne me bohot delayy kardiyaa; also sorry for pissing you out in OAT that night mera intention nahi that (I was into the other one) :v 
Okayy permutations of Kai, you're one of the most likable persons I've met. Like your casual outfits and perpetual nonchalance. Loved your stash hideout and your lessons on Gravity. We've always sort of had accidental encounters but they've been more than occasional and always pleasant. Mumbai was a blast, I feel kind of guilty for ditching you guys the second day but oh well, at least we had a fancy time at that ridiculously expensive place. We should definitely go there again. I'm buying. Anytime ArunK - hit me up, always down to hang out with you. :)
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
First year me jab aaye the pehli baar college tab kaafi interesting interactions rahe bhai apne. Baaki toh yaar tere liye respect hai kaafi. Tune kaafi biases aur odds ko beat kara hai. Antaragni me kaafi kaam kiya tune, aur overall acha nikala bhai. Apne wing me hangouts toh ho hi jaate the, milenge jab bulla katt jayega aaram se bhai! 
All the best!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Chandu bhaiyaa, salaam!
College khatam ho gaya par apni yaari nahi hogi <3 Teri meri school life aisi rahi hai ki dono relate badiya kar paaten hain ek dusre se, isiliye vibe easily kar gaye bhai apan :P College ki bakchodi bhi saath me hui hi hai bohot.. Teacher's ke addhe se Mahashivratri ke prasad tak apne 4 saal bade rangeen rahe hain yaar! Convex Optimization me toh maza hi aa gaya tha (mujhe); shayad course toh apna wahi tha sath me. Antaragni me bakchodi bhi bharpoori ki thi. Hall 5 ke chatt wale bonfire bade yaad aate hain yaar, har winter sochta hu kaash wapas ja pata sabke sath udher :') Triund me tune Tyrion ki tarah muta tha uski video hai mere paas, teri shadi me teri biwi ko dikhaunga.. 4 saal ache rahe hain yaar, tere jaise dost wing me mile ye toh meri achi kismat thi. Milte rahenge, call karte rehna beech beech me bhai!
Tera Apna,
Kothari.
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
*drumroll* best of all worlds Neil Shirude!
For the first few years there I think we were just acquaintances but last last me kaaafi ache dost ho gaye apan bhai! Conversations have always been amazing with you and I always learn something new. Pune aane ka bada mann tha yaar COVID spike ke chalte hi reh gaya mera poora mann tha aane ka bhai. Hope tu apni maid se bohot zyada kaam nahi karwa raha hai thoda rest diya kar yaar xD Tu Mumbai/Pune rahega jab tak apna milna ho jayega bhai koi tension nahi hai. TV shows se leke blogs aur books sab cheez pe apan vibe kiye hain. I think apni intellectual frequency kaafi match karti hai (although teri CPI merese bohot zyada hai _/\_ ). Bhai MS jaake insider trading karna bhai London desk hoga tera mai Europe me rahunga :P
Europe trip banani hai bhai apne wale group ki 100% no excuses. Cheers man to the years we've had but more than that looking forward to the years to come. Startup karna hai bhai sath me please please please.
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: Priyal you are soo not the person you look like on student search (and I mean that in the best possible, yet absolutely mocking sort of way). Sorry for getting you to bear TRC's course (but A laga hoga I hope so not all that sorry). We've come a long way from Prashant Bagad's Introduction to Philosophy to Lalit's Philosophy of Science (yaar wasn't he a cutie!) Campus me hote toh pakka HSS karte koi philosophy ka sath me firse. End me mera campus aana reh hi gayaa but yes that just means we'll have to do our plan some other time (kyuki karenge zarur mana mat karna). Talking to you is kinda fun and pretty effortless, so lets keep the ball rolling! :D
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Bhai <3
One of the most unusually began but closely cherished friendships! What a time its been. From long long long conversations to long long puffs to a long metro ride to you running Bhatia's room that time xD.. you're pretty okay man. From a major sell-off you've had a good bull run these 4 years (and Im somewhat jealous of that trajectory) but happy things worked out for you. Sorry I ditched those US plans,, should have met up but its not like that the end hum toh milte rahenge hi. Thank you for being a part of my IITK life, you're a good friend Ayush!

also fucker chalo kahin abhi plan banate hain jaane se pehle.
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: I have no clue how we first got to know each other (possibly through Dewansh) but I think at some point you just became a familiar person. Seen you spend long days and nights in KD working sincerely through college (which is more than what I can say for most of our batchmates, including myself). Glad to have interacted with you over the years, hopefully, that will continue. Keep going man, I think your sincerity and persistence will outlive all the one-off bakchodi in the world.
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: Hello Sir, I think most of our interactions have been limited to CSE/career/etc and we've had fewer personal or social interactions. I'm sad that is the case, you seem like a nice guy. Anyway, I probably won't be able to say anything on the professional front that you don't already know - You're insanely genius dude, hands down no exaggeration. I think you've already had an innate drive in you before you ever came to IITK, and its been enlightening to have witnessed that. You're spot on and I have no doubt you will achieve greatness. Keep in touch, keep educating us muggles. Ranchi is not far away milte hain kabhi scene bane toh!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: Balllu sirrrr!! You have been a constant throughout my IITK journey even before you were in CSE. One of the most humble, down to earth, practical and intelligent people I know. Amazing discussions, unlimited phone calls, 100s of screen shares and all the course credits calculation and balancing. Bhai IITK life would not have been the same without you. Apne ko thode pizzas aur khane the UC me aur thodi bhakti badhani this shivji ki bhai. COVID toh tere bina nikalta hi nahi bhai. Apne thode social groups alag the college me warna kaaafi zyada hangout karne. Lets meet soon and party!!! Also lets smack some boogie ;)
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: Aise bohot zyada toh nahi hangout kiye apan, par occassionally bulla katt jata tha kabhi academic area me kabhi chaat ke thele pe. Social media hai toh baaten bhi ho hi jaati thi, tu banda badiya hai yaar. UC me tu Madhur saale pizza khane jaate the, kabhi mujhe bhi le chalte tum haramkhoron toh kya bigad jaata. Either way, have fun bhai. Keep in touch! :)
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: Aaayyyee maal, chikne kaisa hai tu. Bhai ye RAC ne BT dedi warna alag maaze karte ye aakhri wale phase me. Bhavy tu toh ekdum constant raha hai 3 saal yaar. Mere paas bohot kuch hai nahi yahan likhne ko kyuki baaten hi itni hain, aur ye tu bhi jaanta hai. Long walks, room talks, IME spot, bandi short, Antaragni wali BT maut. Bhul gaya toh gaand maar lunga. call karte rehna, kuch plans banate hain aage ke. Love u smile <3
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Lal bhai pranam!
Mishraji ne hi introduce kiya hoga hum dono ko, wo first year me Jharkhand circle banane ke enthu me rehte the. Jharkhand Union ke slack pe toh hoga hi tu bhi. Even though we did not have a common social group, CSE aur Mishraji ne dosti toh kara hi di. Apni random conversations ho hi jaati thi beech beech me, career se leke dating tak. I still dont know why you were stalking my ex, she was sure I had something to do with it :P Anyway for full discolsure, you didnt have a chance with her yaar and neither did I lol. Bakchodi karte rehna, badiya software systems bana, milte rahenge!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: God of Disciple and Theory. Shringi sir aapka naam toh IITK aane se pehle hi legend tha. And you have well lived up to that name. College ke 4 saal tujhe shayad hi kabhi apne schedule ko violate karte dekha hai maine, right down to the day and time of when you can have a samosa. Truly impressed, because obviously, I was never the kind of guy who could do this even for a day. Aur bhai Satya sir ke tough courses 2nd year me hi chaap raha that tu toh... Baaki bhai all the best for future Fields Medal and Turing Award and Godel Prize. WIll proudly tell people I went to uni with that guy.
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
BHaiiii Dewansh! Pehle pehle toh binn baap ke bhai aur wingie hi the apan, par Apni existential vibes kaaafi milti hain bhai. Tere room ke posters ekdum fab thay. Thanks for all the times tune Cuppa mania banane ke liye kettle diya apna. Mujhe lagta hai CSE me hoke bhi apan CSE ke bahar ek dusre ko zyada jaante the, pata nahi kyu aisa tha. Either way, masti toh kari hi hai kaafi humne wing me bonfires aur parties aur nashe. GPL lete lete reh gaye tumlog bhai meri xD COVID nahi hua hota toh mujhe lagta hai jaan hi le li hoti tum logon ne GPL ke naam pe :P
Sath bane rehna bhai, college aur wing khatam toh bhul matt jana.. teri instagram stories pe reply karta rahunga mai, asehi controvery karte rehna ;)
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Student search pe Mr. Bean ki photo tu hi daal sakta hai bhai. Badiya rahe hain 4 saal wing me.. hum dono waise koi alag se bohot baaten toh nahi hi karte the par wing ka context tha hamesha wo acha tha. Kevlin ko tujhse marwane me mazza bohot aata tha aur Madhur ko jo tune jaadu dediya tha wo uss photo me perfectly captured hai jo hum sabke paas hamesha rahegi hi xD 
Baaki toh yaar kya bolu, you're okay man! Tune cheezon ko chill leke bhi acha kiya hai and I think that is really an example for me to realize that maybe not taking everything so rigorously is okay. Taale bohot tode hain humne, maybe that was cool! Trip banate hain firse ek bhai tere calculations dekhne me bada mazza aata hai :P
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: CHM101 was where it began right? No, I think it was NCL. Its been bittersweet with you Dishaa, we've regularly bumped into each other at college and tumhare saath bulla kaatna aasan that hamesha hi. We should definitely get more "shots" on the kulfi next time. Do you remember how Kevlin got freaked out when we were watching Friends in my room first year me xD Well, at the end of these 4 years looking back I definitely only really remember the sweet and I hope that's how you see things too. Either way, it's been swell. Keep in touch! :)
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
DRA.
Its been a fun 4 years with you man. I think we got to know each other pretty early over ABS and you've always been this private yet curiously driven fellow. I like that about you. Your hard work is anyway commendable ( 8 straight Dassas, like seriously wtf man!) but you wrote a book! Thats beyond amazing and honestly pretty cool. When you hit on girls at a bar don't say you're a software engineer, tell them you're an author I'm pretty sure that's gonna work wonders. You probably never realized but you've taught me a lot and I am grateful for that. Never seen you cut any corners, which is why I have no doubt you will do amazing in life. I have nothing but respect for you. Mujhe bhul mat jaana plis kripa banaye rakhna.
Baaten karte rahenge asehi randomly..
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
HMMMM GJ mere paas abhi bhi teri Tshirt hai yaar. Wo toh tujhe ab Europe aana padega lene ke liye warna meri. You're undoubtedly one of the most genuine people I Know. Sorry tujhe Dandi se nahi mila paaya par tune aise bhi bohot free ki treat khaayi hai toh compalin mat karna. Late night talks, long walks, bakwas (and achi) movies, saari duniya ka RR aur tera conventional norms ko question karne ka tareeka, everything has been fun. I have no doubt we will continue to stay great friends :)
Tune kaise taise karte karte chaap diya hai college end me so very proud of you; I still remember all your concerns and worries about how things will turn out and I the only thing I'm going to say is "I told you so!".
Have fun Gunjan, meet soon :))
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Ghisu mere bhai!!!! Yaar tune mujhe usi din impress kardiya tha jab maine dekha ki tune mere JEE level of paper utilization ko double se bhi zyada optimize kardiya tha by overwriting blue ink with black. Tune birthday pe wing ko BBQ me treat deke alag hi mazze kara diye the sabke bhai I think uss chakkar me apni wing treats ke standards ache set hogye. Tu kaafi kaafi kaafi zyada hardworking hai yaar kaise karleta hai itna pata nahi. Teri fitness alag level hai bhai mera bag leke tune trekk kardiya tha mai khudko hi nahi utha pa raha tha! Do you remember tere ek birthday me alag level gandd macha di thi wing me humne (with eggs and all)? Uss din bina baat ke bohoton ki GPL hui thi mai bach gaya tha fir bhi kismat se. 4 saal yaar apna toh constant hi raha hai kaafi time, balki kuch din baat nahi hone se mai hi tere room chalaya aaya karta tha ki kya chal raha hai baata. Sorry yaar teri bandi wale scene me mai help nahi kar saka, par tu itna motivated tha hi nahi rectify karne ko warna karte apan pakka! Cold drink kum peeya kar bhai marr jayega (JK tu bohot fit hai). Mujhe lagta hai thoda mujhe khelna zyada chahiye tha tumlog wing wale jab khelte the basketball ya football mai kaafi kum aaya usme thoda regret hota hai. baaki toh yaar itss been very very nice with you, tera Vedant ka phone churana aur chats padhna, wing ko innocently irritate karna kaafi badiya tha sab yaar. Wo wing waale din jo sath me bulla kaat te the bohot yaad aate hain :') Milte rahenge, ghar aaunga mai pakka!
Love u bro!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: Hows the Kej doing? I hope good. Alright man so I think maine, tune Ayush aur Akshay ne kaafi bakchodi kari hai saath me. Bojack S5E6, ultimate booze, premier nashe aur mess me unlimited debates. Sahi hai yaar tu ekdum full of energy and sparkle. Asehi rehna. Mere paas gyaan bohot hai jab chahiye call kar lena :P Na chahiye toh bhi karna bhai baaten toh hain hi bohot. Hope tera wo chakkar sort out ho gaya hoga, 2nd year me humne kaafi baat kari thi uspe. Oh right uske baad tu alag gali me ghuma tha firse xD (dm agar ishara nahi samjha toh). All right man, have fun keep it simple stay silly.
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Bc IITK me mujhse zyada RR toh tu hi karta hoga shayad. poker king hai bhai tu naam badal badal ke chutiyaa kaat ta hai. RR kar kar ke bhi pel ke CPI laata hai aur ab pel ke note bhi layega (IPO alert). Kitne din paper trading karega bhai. Apan dono aise koi emotional level pe bohot connect nahi kiye hain but ache close-knit friend circle me 4 saal sath me toh rahe hain. BHai ek regret hai Madhur ko apan SnT ke liye aur nahi chadha sake thoda push karte thoda fukate maan jaata shayad wo xD
baaki apna toh milna hona chahiye, aur hota rahega. Ache headphones lele bhai please kab tak mute pe rahega.
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Keshav my man, let me first tell you that I am shocked by your humbleness. Few people can be soo intelligent yet so extremely humble. I cannot think of anyone but you, and the irony is I am proud of the fact that we are friends. You are an unbelievably amazing human being. You are smart, talented, dedicated, focused, and extremely hardworking. Without any exaggeration, I think I'm lucky we ended up at the same IIT and our paths crossed (warna kya pata tu rank maar ke IITB chala gaya hota). 
Dont worry about keeping in touch with me, I will ping you regularly from time to time. Keep giving gyaan, hopefully I will learn to be more humble from you. Baaki CSE ka ek poora saal toh humne sath me hi nikala hai, mai semex pe nahi jaata toh aur time niaklta undoubtedly sath me. Thank you man for always helping. Final year hota toh kaaafi zyada bakchodi karwata mai tujhse you have no idea mere poorer plans the. MIlte hain kabhi aur thode mazze karte hain bhai! :)
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Okay Kevlin, here's the deal - I still remember meeting you the first day of college, this scared guy from Patna out into the big big world of bullshit and starlight. Let me first tell you I am immensely proud of the person you have become after 4 years. I would like to think I had some part to play in that though I definitely cannot (and should not take credit for all of it). You are the perfect example of how the IIT system takes in unfettered young individuals and makes them ready for the world. I could not be more proud, as a friend as a brother as a roommate. C110 was an amazing experience and you and Vedant were amazing roommates. I have always found inspiration in your journey and I think it has helped me in getting by when I was abroad. 
Humlogon ne jo wing me bulla kaata hai saalon saal wo toh alag hi level raha hai. Tere Ramji hamesha tere saath rahe hain, aur tu 4 saal baad acha nikal raha hai college se. Dhoni toh chalo chutiya hi hai :P humlog definitely touch me rahenge, C110 will stay alive, saalon baad IITK wapas jaayenge mai tu Vedant C110 me ek din shivbhakti karenge.

Shadi me bulana bhai teri jaldi ho jayegi shayad? I reckon apne wing me Dishant (Rajasthan) ke baad sabse pehle teri hi hogi :P
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
kushgpt my man, what a blast its been. Apna wo special trip reh gaya kabhi sath me Kasol chalo ek alag duniya dikhata hu tujhe wahan! AFAIR maine tujhe fukwaya bhi tha pehli baar :P
Alrighty, bhai I think we got to know each other through PClub, but over time became really good friends. Heres to the 100s of lunch(s)/dinners at ChicBlast, to being stressed of the same things as pclub coordis, to hiding pizzas in NCL during blackbox and to hours and hours of endless discussions and rants in KD/RM. Hoping these days are not over and that Stanford or EPFL, we will continue to stay in touch and possibly even do all of those things yet again. I think we are in way too many common social media groups to lose touch but lets keeeep in touch. Also I think we had the coolest club t-shirt of all time during our tenure!
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Jaaaneman jaanejahan jaane tamanna! Bhai tu mera bromance hai. It was a happy stoke of luck ki tu mujhe wingie mila warna shayad itna zyada acha dost nahi hota mera aaj ek. Mujhe lagta hai maine IITK ki majority life happenings tujhe hi batayi hai sabse pehle. Do you remember December 2019 before I went to MPI, what a night that was man :') Sorry I broke your laptop that day lol. Bhai raat raat rolls aur dominos se pizza mangwana. First year me shorts me thand me 2 bje Crown burgur jaana, humne toh sath me kitna kuch kiya hai yaar! Tu acha aadmi hai thoda zyada hi sabse bohot achi dosti hai teri isiliye silently har friend circle me all powerful ho jaata hai (although ab maine bhatia aur nikunj ne ye realize kar liya hai :P ) Apna poker table acha set ho gaya hai yaar isko chodenge nahi saalon saal chalayenge! Baaki Covid me ghar pe scene sath me banane ka maza hi aur raha hai yaar XD 
Madhur you have truly been an amazing friend and an indisposable part of my IITK journey. Also good that tune end me Dual drop kar hi diya tujhe kitna samjhaya tha ki pointless hai tere liye :P Bhai SnT Secy banna tha yaar tujhe tu khada hota hum bana hi dete bhai kyu nahi hua. Know that you will always be in my thoughts and prayers and I hope you find a girl soon (or are you more interested in Dikshant?) Europe aao bhai ghumne chalte hain amsterdam. Eastern Europe me *** ka precursor mil jata hai easily udher pure milega bhai mazza aayega! Milte hain jald hi! Time series yaad hai na kya bakchod nikala tha humne xD Presentation lol.
Tera apna,
Kothari
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text:
Mayur tu bhai Hero hai! 4 saal sath me bulla kaat kaat ke nikla hai, tune aur Vedant ne hi mujhe nasheeli duniya se introduce karaya tha agar yaad ho tujhe toh xD Bhai jitni baar apan sath me stone hote the tu hamesha hi constantly check kar raha hota tha ki "tujhe kuch feel ho raha hai? ho raha hai?" bhai kaafi funny tha wo par mazza aata tha xD Thanks for hooking me up with Tindal for the next level thing, kaafi badiya tha wo. Bhai tujhe mai sutta fukana toh nahi chudwa saka tune mujhe maal sikha diya xD Bhai badiya raha hai IITK ka time sath me, I really wish tu Sath me trip pe chala hota kaafi maza aata mai -ve me roll kar raha tha bhai udher! CBot forever bhai milte rehna, sabki shaadi me aayenge aur chupke se mehfil jamayenge bhai!
Peace out bro :D
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari

text: In a 1:16 sex ratio in our batch I had very few female friends and you were one of them. Hum dono aise alag se bohot hangout toh nahi kiye hian but common friends, places me kaafi beaten toh kiye hi hain. I am not sure tu final sem me friendly se 420 friendly hui thi ya nahi par hui thi toh maine miss kardiya yaar, you make very nice insta reels and watching you dance high would have been entertaining! Apan randomly college me mil jaate the toh beaten toh kaafi kar hi lete the, teri vibe botot achi hai Medha stay like this always! Hopefully fir asehi kisi common context me milenge and it will be just as easy for us to hangout as it has always been. Also thank you for clearing out my Facebook friend requests list in ChicBlast lol I had not touched it for years! :P

text:

text:

text:
60,000+ Whatsapp messages in 2 odd years (maybe another 200-300 odd hours of calls at least?). By any measure that's quite a lot Pratigya! Despite all ups and downs, you've been an extremely non-trivial part of my IITK journey. Endless gossip, random conversations (sometimes unbelievably so), non-stop bakwas about anything and everything on God's green Earth, and all those walks across campus. I think in retrospect there's a lot to remember, a lot to laugh and cry about, and a lot to reminisce about. I hope you liked Calvin and Hobbes (or at least I hope you read half of it xD ). I could never get you to read many books nor watch some of my favourite shows but if you ever want to (or for that matter talk about random things again), you know where to find me! 
Alright Pratigya, I don't have a lot to write here, I think you know.
Its been real! :)

P.S. - Someday I will collect that Hard Drive
P.P.S. - Scroll through our Whatsapp media toh find 100s of embarrassing pictures :P
author: Yugesh Ajit Kothari
